title: Rob Gulmann
text:
Hello! I’m Rob Gulmann, a final-year Business Studies student specialising in Data Analytics at Dublin City University. I am a generalist with a passion for technology, finance and entrepreneurship. On this website I will share projects and insights.



Projects & Case Studies – Data Analytics, Machine Learning, and more.
Blog Posts – Insights on my life as a final year college student.
Resources & Tools – Helpful links for Quarto, Python, and Git.

🚀 Explore and feel free to connect!
